649:- The launcher hardening pattern evolved in two steps: first fix Cloudflare Tunnel route order so `/assets/*` reaches the entrance service before other routes, then add new service routes only when the service is actually Mac-hosted, localhost-bound, and protected by both Cloudflare Access and the app's own auth. [Task 7]
